---
By: Han Shan
Source:
  ISBN: 9781590303993
  Locus:
    Page: 96
  Title: The Poetry of Enlightenment
  Translator: Sheng Yen
---
In the flash of one thought
My turbulent mind came to a rest.
The inner and the outer,
The senses and their objects,
Are thoroughly lucid.
In a complete turnabout
I smashed the Great Emptiness.
The ten thousand manifestations
Arise and disappear
Without any reason.
